To create a skybox using the Mandelbrot image, we can use an `a-sky` entity in A-Frame and set its `src` attribute to the Mandelbrot image. A skybox will give the effect of a large, surrounding image that acts as the background of the scene.

Here's the updated code implementing this feature:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
